    <item>
      <title>欧盟对特朗普全球关税罢工的“强大计划”的重视</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/eu-readies-strong-plan-against-trump-s-global-tariff-strike</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟表示，如果唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）遵循他的威胁，将利用广泛的选择来对美国进行报复，并在本周本周在集团上征收所谓的互惠关税。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/eu-readies-strong-plan-against-trump-s-global-tariff-strike</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Apr 2025 07:39:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列说，贝鲁特郊区罢工目标的真主党特工</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/israel-says-hezbollah-operative-targeted-in-beirut-suburb-strike</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自11月停产以来，以色列在黎巴嫩首次袭击黎巴嫩首都几天后，以色列在贝鲁特郊区进行了一次空袭，该空袭是针对真主党特工的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/israel-says-hezbollah-operative-targeted-in-beirut-suburb-strike</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Apr 2025 02:16:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
